---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout 
  title="About Wayne Leighton - Author & Business Consultant" 
  description="Learn about Wayne Leighton, renowned author and business consultant with over 15 years of experience helping leaders achieve sustainable growth."
>
  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          About Wayne Leighton
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Transforming leaders and organizations through practical wisdom, 
          proven strategies, and sustainable business practices.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-16">
        <!-- Author Photo & Bio -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-8">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
              <div class="md:w-1/3">
                <img 
                  src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472099645785-5658abf4ff4e?w=300&h=300&fit=crop&crop=face" 
                  alt="Wayne Leighton"
                  class="w-full aspect-square object-cover rounded-lg"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="md:w-2/3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
                  Leadership Through Purpose
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                  Wayne Leighton is a renowned author, speaker, and business consultant with over 15 years of 
                  experience helping leaders and organizations achieve sustainable growth. His unique approach 
                  combines practical business strategies with mindful leadership principles.
                </p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                  Having worked with Fortune 500 companies and emerging startups alike, Wayne brings a 
                  wealth of real-world experience to his writing and consulting practice.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Philosophy -->
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">Philosophy & Approach</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                Wayne believes that true leadership isn't about commanding from the topâ€”it's about 
                empowering others to reach their full potential while building sustainable, purpose-driven 
                organizations that make a positive impact on the world.
              </p>
              <p>
                His methodology focuses on three core pillars: <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Mindful Leadership</strong>, 
                <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Sustainable Growth</strong>, and 
                <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Digital Innovation</strong>. This holistic approach 
                has helped countless leaders navigate the complexities of modern business while staying true to their values.
              </p>
              <p>
                Through his books, Wayne shares practical frameworks and proven strategies that readers can 
                implement immediately, backed by extensive research and real-world case studies.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Experience -->
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">Experience & Background</h2>
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="border-l-4 border-primary-600 pl-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Business Consulting</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  15+ years helping organizations transform their leadership culture and achieve sustainable growth. 
                  Clients include Fortune 500 companies, tech startups, and non-profit organizations.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="border-l-4 border-primary-600 pl-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Speaking & Training</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Keynote speaker at major business conferences and leadership summits. Has trained over 10,000 
                  executives and emerging leaders across various industries.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="border-l-4 border-primary-600 pl-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Research & Writing</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Author of 5 bestselling books on leadership and business strategy. Regular contributor to 
                  Harvard Business Review, Forbes, and other leading business publications.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <!-- Quick Stats -->
          <div class="bg-primary-50 dark:bg-primary-900/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Quick Facts</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Books Published:</span>
                <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">5</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Years Experience:</span>
                <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">15+</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Leaders Trained:</span>
                <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">10,000+</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Countries Reached:</span>
                <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">25+</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Awards -->
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Recognition</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Business Book of the Year 2023</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Top 40 Under 40 Business Leaders</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Excellence in Leadership Training</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Contact -->
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Connect</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <a href="#" class="flex items-center space-x-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 hover:text-primary-600 dark:hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M22.46 6c-.77.35-1.6.58-2.46.69.88-.53 1.56-1.37 1.88-2.38-.83.5-1.75.85-2.72 1.05C18.37 4.5 17.26 4 16 4c-2.35 0-4.27 1.92-4.27 4.29 0 .34.04.67.11.98C8.28 9.09 5.11 7.38 3 4.79c-.37.63-.58 1.37-.58 2.15 0 1.49.75 2.81 1.91 3.56-.71 0-1.37-.2-1.95-.5v.03c0 2.08 1.48 3.82 3.44 4.21a4.22 4.22 0 0 1-1.93.07 4.28 4.28 0 0 0 4 2.98 8.521 8.521 0 0 1-5.33 1.84c-.34 0-.68-.02-1.02-.06C3.44 20.29 5.7 21 8.12 21 16 21 20.33 14.46 20.33 8.79c0-.19 0-.37-.01-.56.84-.6 1.56-1.36 2.14-2.23z"/>
                </svg>
                <span>@wayneleighton</span>
              </a>
              <a href="#" class="flex items-center space-x-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 hover:text-primary-600 dark:hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
                </svg>
                <span>LinkedIn</span>
              </a>
              <a href="mailto:wayne@wayneleightonbooks.com" class="flex items-center space-x-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 hover:text-primary-600 dark:hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>Email</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 rounded-xl p-8 text-center text-white">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">
          Ready to Transform Your Leadership?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6 text-primary-100">
          Explore Wayne's collection of transformative books and start your journey today.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="/shop" 
          class="bg-white text-primary-600 hover:bg-gray-100 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors inline-flex items-center"
        >
          Browse All Books
          <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>